  <sect2>
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Install the package by running the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>patch -p1 -i ../tar-&tar-version;-manpage-1.patch &amp;&amp;
FORCE_UNSAFE_CONFIGURE=1 \
./configure --disable-nls &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Finally, generate the man page and place it in the proper location:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>perl tarman &gt; /usr/local/share/man/man1/tar.1</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

